WEBVTT

00:00:01.000 --> 00:00:08.267
They told us the grid would take a century to rebuild. That the cost was too high. The politics, too fragile.

00:00:11.500 --> 00:00:15.767
But yesterday, we simply... rewrote the physics of the possible.

00:00:19.000 --> 00:00:22.000
No budgets. No borders. Just the Aether Web.

00:00:25.500 --> 00:00:31.233
A superconducting planetary lattice, spun from starlight. Earth, finally synchronized.

